      "id": "PopularPost30694",
      "post_content": "This card is extremely popular in Storm decks such as Ad-Naseuam + Tendrils.  \n  \nYou need to use its effect when an ability is on the stack that allows you to draw more cards, such as [Ad Naseuam](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ad Naseuam). Then you get the mana and refill your hand.  \n  \nAnother great use for this card is with [Yawgmoth's Will](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Yawgmoth's Will):  \n  \nSwamp; Lion's Eye Diamond; Dark Ritual; Yawg Will. Then crack Diamond...pull it back with Will...use it again. Then reuse your dark ritual. 8 black mana floating turn 1 with a graveyard full of goodies you can play as though they were in your hand. Don't even need reanimator...",
      "posted_by": "kitsunewarlock",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost30694\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">This card is extremely popular in Storm decks such as Ad-Naseuam + Tendrils.<br/><br/>You need to use its effect when an ability is on the stack that allows you to draw more cards, such as <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ad Naseuam\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ad Naseuam\">Ad Naseuam</a>.  Then you get the mana and refill your hand.<br/><br/>Another great use for this card is with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Yawgmoth's Will\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Yawgmoth's Will\">Yawgmoth's Will</a>:<br/><br/>Swamp; Lion's Eye Diamond; Dark Ritual; Yawg Will.  Then crack Diamond...pull it back with Will...use it again.  Then reuse your dark ritual.  8 black mana floating turn 1 with a graveyard full of goodies you can play as though they were in your hand.  Don't even need reanimator...</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '30694'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy486\">kitsunewarlock</span>\r\n                                (10/19/2009 2:16:33 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u0