    {
      "id": "PopularPost231355",
      "post_content": "The oracle text is weird and most people eont understand why. If it was a full unrestricted mana ability it would be practically black lotus  \n  \nSpells are declared and put on the stack, then the player activates mana abilities to pay for it. You can cast a card from your hand then choose to pay with LED if it was unrestricted.  \n  \nYou would also be able to use it in dredge and activate it while dredging to discard dredgers if you have multiple draws stacked.  \n  \nThe instant priority ruling prevents all those shinanegans.   \n  \nRemember, you cant pay for Join Forces commander cards with LED. You cant pay for mana leak once you declared to pay; must be poped in response to mana leak if you want to do it.",
      "posted_by": "BattleFish",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost231355\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">The oracle text is weird and most people eont understand why. If it was a full unrestricted mana ability it would be practically black lotus<br/><br/>Spells are declared and put on the stack, then the player activates mana abilities to pay for it. You can cast a card from your hand then choose to pay with LED if it was unrestricted.<br/><br/>You would also be able to use it in dredge and activate it while dredging to discard dredgers if you have multiple draws stacked.<br/><br/>The instant priority ruling prevents all those shinanegans. <br/><br/>Remember, you cant pay for Join Forces commander cards with LED. You cant pay for mana leak once you declared to pay; must be poped in response to mana leak if you want to do it.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '231355'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy58078\">BattleFish</span>\r\n                                (3/4/2012 9:54:39 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl0